<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Bride To Be Party Games</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bride_to_be_games.css" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="hero-bride_to_be_games">
    <div class="hero-text-bride_to_be_games">
      <h1>Bride To Be Party Games</h1>
      <p>Create unforgettable memories with fun and luxurious games curated for the bride-to-be.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="intro-bride_to_be_games">
    <p class="intro-line1">Planning a bridal celebration that's both fun and elegant?</p>
    <p class="intro-line2">Our handpicked party games ensure laughter, love, and meaningful connections. Explore unique activities that bring joy to every guest and make the bride feel extra special.</p>
  </section>  

<!-- Games Section -->
<section class="games-section">

    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/57/f6/a1/57f6a1eefe1736892667d4d004ab28ea.jpg" alt="Who Knows the Bride Game">
      <h2>Who Knows the Bride Best?</h2>
      <p>A fun quiz game to discover who knows the bride the best — with sweet surprises and lots of laughs.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Prepare quirky questions about the bride</li>
        <li>Distribute answer sheets to guests</li>
        <li>Go through each question aloud</li>
        <li>Highest scorer wins a prize</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  
    <div class="game-card">
        <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/a3/f4/27/a3f4273446915bfd073e947d01191268.jpg" alt="Guess the Bride's Wedding Dress Game">
        <h2>Guess the Bride's Wedding Dress</h2>
        <p>Engage guests in an imaginative game by predicting the bride’s stunning wedding attire.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide paper and pencils to guests</li>
          <li>Ask them to sketch their idea of the bride's wedding dress</li>
          <li>The bride selects her favorite sketch</li>
          <li>Winner receives a memorable prize</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
  
    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/43/71/7e/43717e73cceccc99f31f0fa01372a9e4.jpg" alt="Memory Lane Game">
      <h2>Memory Lane</h2>
      <p>A heartwarming journey through shared memories — perfect for emotional and joyful moments.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Ask guests to write a special memory with the bride</li>
        <li>Read them out anonymously</li>
        <li>The bride guesses who wrote each one</li>
        <li>Great way to bond and reminisce</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  
    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/fd/d4/fb/fdd4fb759a3ecad14b164a17148b79c7.jpg" alt="Find the Ring Game">
      <h2>Find the Ring (Hidden Hunt)</h2>
      <p>Turn the venue into a mini scavenger hunt by hiding toy rings or decorative items.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Hide small ring props around the party area</li>
        <li>Guests search to find as many as possible</li>
        <li>Set a time limit</li>
        <li>The one with the most rings wins a prize</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  
    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/2e/f5/11/2ef511487f36eecc2cfe9107e201525f.jpg" alt="Bridal Bingo Game">
      <h2>Bridal Bingo</h2>
      <p>An elegant take on classic bingo — filled with bridal-themed prompts and surprises.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Prepare bingo cards with bridal activities (e.g. “bride talks about fiancé”, “guest cries”)</li>
        <li>Distribute cards and pens</li>
        <li>Mark off boxes as the moments happen</li>
        <li>First to complete a row or full card wins</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  
    <div class="game-card">
      <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/736x/d6/bf/fb/d6bffbde625275dabb580bd729140ea9.jpg" alt="Bridal Mad Libs Game">
      <h2>Bridal Mad Libs</h2>
      <p>A hilarious word game where guests fill in blanks for a silly bridal story — results are always a hit!</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Create short bridal-themed stories with blank spaces</li>
        <li>Ask guests for random nouns, verbs, adjectives, etc.</li>
        <li>Insert the words and read aloud the results</li>
        <li>Everyone laughs at the unpredictable stories</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  
  </section>
  

</body>
</html>
